product.availability: Usually Ships in 2 to 3 Business Days
product.productFeatures:
No need to iron, this soft, 100% cotton dress shirt is specially engineered to resist wrinkles so it stays looking crisp and pulled-together.
Button down collar. Chest pocket. Adjustable double-button barrel cuffs.
Button placket.
Interlined collar for a crisp finish.
Triangular gusset at side seams for durability.
Shirttail hem.
product.productDescriptionAbovePricing: No need to iron, this soft, 100% cotton dress shirt is specially engineered to resist wrinkles so it stays looking crisp and pulled-together.
